title: Lois' wholemeal seeded bread
ingredients: ['300ml water', '2 tablespoons margarine, softened', '250g white bread flour', '125g wholemeal flour', '3 tablespoons dried milk powder', '2 tablespoons caster sugar', '1 1/2 teaspoons salt', '2 teaspoons bread machine yeast', '5 tablespoons pumpkin and sunflower seed mix']
